== Aglam == 
[[Addud]] n llama aglawan yettawaṭ gar n 109 ar 119 cm , d 120 ar 125 cm ɣer [[aqerru|yixef]], [[Azul|azuk-is]] iga gar n 130 ar 155 kg. Tla (tesɛa) aṭas n [[taduṭṭ]], Ma yella win iṭɣaren (iqerrben) ar llama ad t-it[[Tisusaf|ssusef]] ɣer [[udem|wudem-is]] s werway n [[učči|wučči]] ur nettwagfeẓ ara 

Llama d aɣersiw ur nli [[ameddis]] s wemgarad n [[alɣem|ulɣem]] d [[Amaynag|umaynag]] [[tiddi (akat)|Tiddi-ynes]] tettawaṭ ar 1,2 m. [[Ini]] n [[azaf|wazaf-is]] d [[aras]] 

== Assaɣ neɣ tazdayt n [[afgan|ufgan]] d llama ==
